"This concludes the tour of the KStars skymap, although we have only scratched the surface of the available features. KStars includes many useful :doc:`astronomy tools  <tools>`, it can directly "
":doc:`control your telescope  <indi>`, and it offers a wide variety of :doc:`configuration and customization options  <config>`. In addition, this Handbook includes the :doc:`AstroInfo Project  "
"<astroinfo>`, a series of short, interlinked articles explaining some of the celestial and astrophysical concepts behind KStars."
